 visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Each draw has its own cut-off and invitation criteria."},{"level":1,"question":"What are police certificates used for?","options":["Criminality screening","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Police certificates support admissibility assessment."},{"level":1,"question":"What are immigration medical exams used for?","options":["Health admissibility assessment","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"IRCC uses medical exams to assess health admissibility."},{"level":1,"question":"What is an enhanced PNP stream?","options":["A provincial stream aligned with Express Entry","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Enhanced nominations connect with Express Entry and can add CRS points."},{"level":1,"question":"What does entering the pool not create by itself?","options":["Permanent resident status","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Entering the pool is not the same as being invited or approved."},{"level":1,"question":"Why keep an Express Entry profile accurate?","options":["Unsupported information can cause refusal or misrepresentation concerns","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"The PR application must support the profile''s claims."},{"level":2,"question":"Which document is needed for foreign education CRS points?","options":["Educational Credential Assessment","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"An ECA is commonly required for points for foreign education."},{"level":2,"question":"What should an employment reference letter include?","options":["Duties, title, dates, hours, salary, and employer details","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Detailed letters help prove skilled work and NOC alignment."},{"level":2,"question":"Why are duties more important than title alone?","options":["NOC matching is based mainly on duties","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Officers compare actual duties to the claimed NOC."},{"level":2,"question":"What if circumstances change after ITA?","options":["The application must remain accurate and eligibility must still be met","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Post-ITA changes can affect CRS, eligibility, and documents."},{"level":2,"question":"What deadline follows an ITA?","options":["A fixed deadline to submit the electronic PR application","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"The account shows the submission deadline."},{"level":2,"question":"What should proof of funds letters show?","options":["Available, transferable, unencumbered settlement money","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Funds must satisfy IRCC settlement-fund requirements."},{"level":2,"question":"Who may not need settlement funds?","options":["A CEC applicant or applicant with qualifying arranged employment where rules allow","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Proof-of-funds exemptions depend on program and employment context."},{"level":2,"question":"What is arranged employment for CRS?","options":["A qualifying valid job offer meeting Express Entry rules","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Not every job offer qualifies for CRS points."},{"level":2,"question":"Why might an LMIA matter for job offer points?","options":["Some offers need LMIA support unless an exemption applies","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Valid job offer rules can require LMIA or qualifying LMIA-exempt status."},{"level":2,"question":"How is Canadian work counted for CEC?","options":["Authorized paid skilled work in Canada","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"CEC requires qualifying Canadian skilled work gained with authorization."},{"level":2,"question":"Which work is excluded from CEC experience?","options":["Unauthorized work","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Unauthorized work cannot be used as qualifying Canadian experience."},{"level":2,"question":"How can part-time work count?","options":["As equivalent experience if it meets program rules","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Part-time hours can count when properly calculated."},{"level":2,"question":"Why calculate dates precisely?","options":["Claiming experience too early can cause refusal","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Eligibility often depends on exact dates, months, and hours."},{"level":2,"question":"How can a spouse''s language test affect CRS?","options":["It may add points for an accompanying spouse","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Spousal factors can change CRS."},{"level":2,"question":"What should be done if a score is inflated before accepting ITA?","options":["Correct or decline if points cannot be supported","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Unsupported CRS claims can cause refusal."},{"level":2,"question":"What proves identity and travel history basics?","options":["Passport pages","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Passports support identity, status history, and travel history."},{"level":2,"question":"Why do police certificate country rules matter?","options":["Requirements depend on where and how long the applicant lived","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Applicants must follow country-specific instructions."},{"level":2,"question":"What is personal history used for?","options":["Accounting for activities without unexplained gaps","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Personal history supports background and consistency review."},{"level":2,"question":"What is a medical instruction process?","options":["A way to complete the required immigration medical exam","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Medical exams are part of PR admissibility screening."},{"level":2,"question":"Which fees are common at PR submission?","options":["Processing fee and right of permanent residence fee","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Express Entry PR applications include government fees."},{"level":2,"question":"Why prepare translations properly?","options":["Non-English or non-French documents need acceptable translations","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Translations must meet IRCC document standards."},{"level":2,"question":"What is a letter of explanation best for?","options":["Clarifying specific document issues or unusual facts","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"It should clarify evidence, not replace eligibility."},{"level":2,"question":"What should be checked after new language results?","options":["Whether CRS and program eligibility changed","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Language results can affect thresholds and ranking."},{"level":2,"question":"Why do PNP nomination conditions matter?","options":["The applicant may need to maintain intent and truthful provincial information","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Federal review continues after nomination."},{"level":2,"question":"How should non-accompanying family be handled?","options":["Disclose them and complete required examinations unless exempted","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Family members must be disclosed even if they are not immigrating."},{"level":3,"question":"What if CRS drops below the draw cut-off after ITA?","options":["The application may be refused if invitation criteria are no longer met","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Applicants must support the score that justified the invitation."},{"level":3,"qu