k experience","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"A PFL allows response to serious concerns."},{"level":3,"question":"What is safest for a borderline NOC claim?","options":["Choose the NOC best supported by duties and evidence","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"The strongest NOC is the one the records support."},{"level":3,"question":"Why track marital-status changes?","options":["They can affect CRS, forms, family admissibility, and documents","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Family composition changes must be disclosed."},{"level":3,"question":"What is a risk with Canadian work gained as a full-time student?","options":["Some student work may be excluded from CEC eligibility","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"CEC has specific exclusions for student work."},{"level":3,"question":"Why do payroll records strengthen work evidence?","options":["They corroborate paid employment, hours, and dates","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Pay records support the genuineness and duration of employment."},{"level":3,"question":"What is the risk of missing the eAPR deadline?","options":["Late or missing documents may lead to rejection or refusal","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Express Entry deadlines are strict."},{"level":3,"question":"Why disclose non-accompanying dependants?","options":["Undisclosed family can create future sponsorship and admissibility problems","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"All family members must be disclosed as required."},{"level":3,"question":"What if claimed CRS points cannot be proven?","options":["Refusal and possible misrepresentation finding","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"The applicant must prove eligibility and claimed points."},{"level":3,"question":"Why do category-based draws require care?","options":["The candidate must meet the specific category criteria","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Category-based invitations rely on additional attributes."},{"level":3,"question":"What if arranged employment ends after ITA?","options":["Job offer points may no longer be valid","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Job offer points depend on continuing qualifying circumstances."},{"level":3,"question":"How should unobtainable documents be handled?","options":["Provide proof of attempts, explanation, and acceptable alternatives if allowed","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Diligent efforts should be documented."},{"level":3,"question":"Why can an old immigration violation affect Express Entry?","options":["It may raise admissibility or credibility concerns","A temporary visitor visa category","A school admissions system","A passport renewal service"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Past compliance can remain relevant."}],"donts":{"dos":["Calculate CRS honestly at intake","Verify TEER/NOC codes","Secure detailed reference letters","Monitor draw trends with client","Only submit PR after ITA"],"donts":["Do not guarantee ITA or PR","Do not inflate work experience","Do not collect full PR fee before ITA","Do not us