ssment","A visitor visa issued for tourism only","An employer-specific LMIA approval","A permanent resident card"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Processing and travel authorization are separate concerns."},{"level":3,"question":"How should a potential non-compliance period be addressed?","options":["Disclose it accurately and provide factual context","A visitor visa issued for tourism only","An employer-specific LMIA approval","A permanent resident card"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Transparency reduces misrepresentation risk and helps explain the record."},{"level":3,"question":"Why can a withdrawn semester matter after graduation?","options":["It may affect continuous study and authorized leave analysis","A visitor visa issued for tourism only","An employer-specific LMIA approval","A permanent resident card"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Graduation alone may not cure every study-history issue."},{"level":3,"question":"Which issue most likely needs legal advice before PGWP submission?","options":["Prior unauthorized work combined with expired status","A visitor visa issued for tourism only","An employer-specific LMIA approval","A permanent resident card"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Multiple compliance problems can affect eligibility and future applications."},{"level":3,"question":"What does officer discretion focus on in complex PGWP files?","options":["Whether evidence proves the requirements are met","A visitor visa issued for tourism only","An employer-specific LMIA approval","A permanent resident card"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"The decision is evidence-based and tied to legal and policy criteria."},{"level":3,"question":"Why should explanation letters be evidence-linked?","options":["They help the officer connect facts to documents","A visitor visa issued for tourism only","An employer-specific LMIA approval","A permanent resident card"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Good explanations clarify the record without replacing proof."},{"level